---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | AltFins">
    <Navigation />
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 pt-[80px]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p>By accessing and using the AltFins platform, you agree to these Terms of Service ("Terms") and our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with these Terms, you may not use the platform.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Use License</h2>
            <p>We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, revocable license to use the AltFins platform for personal, non-commercial purposes only.  This license does not allow you to alter, distribute, or sell any part of the platform or its content.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. User Conduct</h2>
            <p>You agree to use the AltFins platform responsibly and legally. This includes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
              <li>Providing accurate information when creating an account.</li>
              <li>Not harming or disrupting the platform or its services.</li>
              <li>Respecting intellectual property rights.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Changes to the Terms</h2>
            <p>We may update these Terms at any time.  Your continued use of AltFins after any changes means you accept the updated Terms.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Termination of Access</h2>
            <p>We may terminate or suspend your access to AltFins at any time, with or without cause. Upon termination, your right to use the platform will end, and you must destroy any downloaded or printed materials.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Disclaimers</h2>
            <p>The information on AltFins is for educational purposes only and is not financial advice. We make no warranty regarding the accuracy, reliability, or completeness of the information.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>AltFins is not liable for any damages arising from your use of the platform. We are not responsible for any third-party tools or resources linked on the platform.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Indemnification</h2>
            <p>You agree to indemnify AltFins from any claims arising out of your use of the platform or violation of these Terms.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Governing Law</h2>
            <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of [Your Jurisdiction].</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Entire Agreement</h2>
            <p>These Terms are the complete agreement between you and AltFins regarding your use of the platform.</p>
          </section>
      
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Contact Information</h2>
            <p>Contact us at [Your Contact Information] with any questions.</p>
          </section>
      
        </div>
      </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
